I"E<p>These days i was busy working on an a project called as Node Twitter.
As the name suggest it is a twitter clone written on node.</p>

<p>Right now it has following functionalities:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Login via Facebook and Github</li>
  <li>Tweet Add, Modify, Delete</li>
  <li>Comment on Tweet</li>
  <li>Favorite a Tweet</li>
  <li>See own and another userâ€™s profile</li>
  <li>Follow another User</li>
</ul>

