<p>I am also planning to add all other features present on twitter one by one. Next would be dashboard(timeline), personal profile, retweet and hashtags.</p>

<p>These features might seem simple but most of them are not that simple and requires some good effort.
Anyways, you can test it here:</p>
<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span>npm <span class="nb">install </span>nwitter
<span class="nv">$ </span>npm start
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>Then open your browser and open <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">http://localhost:3000</code>.</p>
